Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.46,0:00:34.68,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Even the world's billions of heartbeats
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.68,0:00:41.60,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Are nothing to you but a fleeting and insignificant question
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.60,0:00:46.65,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}We may be trapped in the past or lament the future
