Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:10.67,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(0,250)}Finitude is what the two clock hands show
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.67,0:01:15.42,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(250,0)}As they point toward a cruel destiny and choice
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.34,0:01:24.56,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(1000,0}And now I cross the boundary between worlds each second
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.56,0:01:29.61,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Because I want to protect that smile of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:36.53,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}And a loop in time without sadness will once again
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.53,0:01:42.79,OP Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}Engulf me, a lonely observer
